<HEADLINE> Philippine President Visits Oman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, June 21 (Xinhua) -- President Fidel Ramos of the
Philippines today began his two-day visit to Oman to boost trade
relations between the two countries, the Omani news agency
reported.
</P>
