<HEADLINE> Moldova Hails Hong Kong's Return to China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, June 22 (Xinhua) -- The Moldovan government welcomes
the forthcoming return of Hong Kong to China and favors the
principles adopted by the Chinese government to reunite the
country through peaceful means, said a report coming from Moldovan
capital of Chisinau today.
</P>
<P>
A press release issued by the press office of the Moldovan
government said the Moldovan government believes that China will
resume the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong on the basis of
the principle "one country, two systems", ending the British
colonial rule there.
</P>
<P>
The Moldovan government hopes that China, which enjoys
high-speed economic development and a culture of long standing,
can solve the problems of Macao and Taiwan as early as possible,
the press release added.  
</P>
</TEXT>
