crisis in the Palestinian-Israeli peace track that derailed in
March when Israel broke ground for a new Jewish settlement in Arab
East Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
Meguid told reporters that he carries a letter signed by both
the Arab League and the Organization of African Unity (OAU) to the
chairman of the U.N. Security Council on Lockerbie crisis.
</P>
<P>
