He said that besides stern action, the situation in the Balkan
state needs monitoring to prevent it from reverting to political
disunity.
</P>
<P>
Leaders at the G7 summit in Denver yesterday passed a
resolution asking the authorities in Bosnia to uphold fully the
right of refugees and displaced persons to return to their
homeland in a peaceful and orderly manner.
</P>
<P>
The Bosnian factions were also required to turn over
individuals indicted for war crimes to the International Criminal
Tribunal.  
