his pre-Wimbledon confidence by winning the Nottingham Open on
Saturday as rain forced the match indoors.
</P>
<P>
The Canadian-born Rusedski powered to an impressive 6-4, 7-5
victory over Karol Kucera, his fourth ATP title.
</P>
